cp - copy files and directories
Executable: /bin/cp.sh
Alias: cp

DESCRIPTION
  Copies files or whole
  directory trees.

USAGE
  cp <source> <destination>
  cp <source> [source...]
     <directory>

NOTES
  Wildcards are expanded
  through fs.find().
  When copying multiple
  sources, the destination
  must already be a
  directory.
